{
  "stem": "5970.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And the crematorium was in the fifth one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "So whenever you heard that somebody was taken to the fifth field, you knew he's never going to come back from there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "I can't remember which number we were, which field.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "But when we arrived in Majdanek, there were very few Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "They've killed most of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "They were the men from our transport, from Radom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "There were the group of girls that I'll talk about in a minute, that were left from the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "Because when they closed the ghetto in Lodz, it was one of the biggest ghettos in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "According to the statistics, there were 200,000 Jews in the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And most of them were taken to Majdanek when they liquidated the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And most of them were killed there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "But out of all these multitudes of people, they selected 100 young women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And they were beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "Each one of them was prettier than the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "And we looked at them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "And couldn't understand what was going on there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "They were well-dressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And they seemed to be well fed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "And they were beautiful, each one and one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "And eventually, we found out what was the story with these girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "First, they were working in the stores where they collected all the jewelry and money and all the things that the people brought with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "And there were masses of stuff there, clothes and jewelry and gold and masses of stuff.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "So they were working with this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "And then, they were working in a German brothel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "They used them for the soldiers who came from the Eastern Front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "That was their work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "And they were wonderful to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "They helped us a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 112,
      "text": "We didn't come in contact with all 100.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
